node.text: @matt_crafton and his family came over to drive the @canamoffroad vehicles around the house. Can Am’s are are tough as they come. Also, to be fair to Matt, it was pretty bent from @conordaly22 last cartwheel which I’m sure contributed 🤔🤦👍

node.text:
Found some footage of getting to ride Kenny Roberts JR’s Suzuki 500! Thanks for letting me borrow your helmet @sundersam !! What a week!
@subarumotorsportsusa @yokohamatire @nitrocircus @thehoonigans #thankyougoodwood @kmcwheels

The @fosgoodwood experience surpassed all of my expectations. From borrowing gear and riding Kenny Roberts JR’s moto gp bike up the hill at speed to sitting passenger with Jimmy McRae in one of Colin’s old Group A Subaru’s to flying a @takeongravity jet pack to racing @traxxas rc cars to a formal dinner in a castle with Duke Charles while we watched The Who play to 30 minutes of the best fireworks display I’ve ever witnessed.. and of course, racing the air slayer gymkhana wrx up the hillclimb! Also, stoked to finally meet the future female mx champion @oliviareynoldsmx and drift champion @jamesdeane130 .
@subarumotorsportsusa @yokohamatire @alpinestars @redbullmotorsports @kmcwheels @kuhl @motul

node.text:
Awesome day at the @fosgoodwood event. Qualified 1st in the hillclimb with my Subaru gymkhana car and got to drive one of Colin McRae’s old Subaru Group A legacys on the rally stage thanks to @dirtfishrally Steve Rimmer. Hopefully Sunday goes as well and we can get a win!
@yokohamatire @kmcwheels @subarumotorsportsusa @nitrocircus @redbullmotorsports @subarumotorsportsusa
